<br>
Just ensure that when you award loot you have some methodology that doesn't focus on a single person as the recipient.<br>
<br>
Even though initially, a long time ago, we equipped a warrior or two to the teeth and those warriors did drop out for a while they came back.<br>
<br>
Take the time to try to focus on getting loot distributed to many of the same class and make sure you also keep the other classes satisfied and make sure you keep trying for harder and more interesting mobs.  You'll see alot of burn out no matter what route you take to accomplish your ends.<br>
<br>
